snippet.title: Cyber Virus | Atari Lynx Collection 1 | Game 4 of 17 | Evercade Handheld
snippet.description:
Finally, a first-person shooter for the Lynx! As one of the last Demolition Ops Guerrillas (DOGs) of War, the hero journeys around the world destroying bio-mechanical monstrosities bent on subjugating the world to their will.

Keep track of your limited ammo, and make sure you don't wander off the edge of the map before completing your mission. Things getting a little too tough for you? Try a cheat code.

Year: 2002
Publisher: Songbird Productions
Genre: FPS
